    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>A gathering of OLPCs</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/424381005/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="A gathering of OLPCs" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/172/424381005_971edcddbb_m.jpg" height="240" width="180" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Several prototypes from the <a href="http://www.laptop.org/">One Laptop Per Child</a> program were brought along for geeks to play with.  While I'm not going to give up my MacBook any time soon, they are beautifully designed for what they're needed to do.</p>
        </p>

