        <h4>BarCampBoston2 Programming Contest topic board</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/424380828/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="BarCampBoston2 Programming Contest topic board" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/188/424380828_10703d8724_m.jpg" height="240" width="180" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>To inspire programmers taking part in the 24-hour Programming Contest, a list of topics was drawn up and ten were drawn at random.</p>

<p>(This board was later amended to say &quot;Convince us that you used at least 4...&quot;)</p>

<p>And no, I have no idea what &quot;BBQ Calculator&quot; means either.</p>
